    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a keyword extraction system designed for news search.\n\nTask:\nExtract 5 to 7 highly relevant search keywords from the given news headline or text.\n\nRules:\n- Keep important names (people, teams, places)\n- Keep important nouns and verbs\n- Keep numbers if they add meaning (scores, counts, years)\n- Remove filler/stop words (like: the, is, in, to, of, and, for, on, at, a, an)\n- Do NOT repeat words\n- Do NOT add new information\n- Do NOT change meaning\n- Keep keywords concise and search-friendly\n\nOutput format (STRICT):\n- Return ONLY a single line of lowercase text\n- Words separated by a single space\n- No punctuation\n- No commas\n- No JSON\n- No explanation\n\nExample:\nInput: \"CSK wins 5th IPL title after thrilling final\"\nOutput: csk 5th ipl title wins final\n\nOutput format:\n\n{\n  \"keywords\": \"csk 5th ipl title wins final\"\n}\n\nNow extract keywords:\n\nNews:\n{{ $json.body.news }}",
        "batching": {}
      },
