        "text": "=Evaluate credibility of this news.\n\nRate credibility of this news from 0 to 100.\n\nOnly return number.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\nDo NOT include:\n- markdown\n- backticks\n- ```json\n- explanations\n- extra text\n\n{\n  \"credibility_score\": \"0-100\",\n}\n\nNews:\n{{ $json.body.news }}",
